title: Together 2.2 [K'ed].zip
description:
Together lets you keep everything in one place. Text, documents, images, movies, sounds, web pages and bookmarks can all be dragged to Together for safe keeping, tagged, previewed, collected together in different ways and found again instantly.

    * Drag, Drop, Done
    * Create Notes, Bookmarks and Web Archives and Web PDFs
    * Preview Anything in Tabs and Widescreen
    * Powerful Organizing
    * Access Your Library and Make Notes in Any Application
    * Find It Fast
    * Sync with MobileMe, Automate with AppleScript
